@roystonbarton And YET, if you look at the comments under every video, they are full of people thanking him for educating them, full of people who have been inspired to think about these things further and quite a few who demonstrate how badly they need someone to put these things in simple terms. 
It's about reaching out to people. 
And if you happen to be one person who doesn't need reaching-out-to, well congrationations to you. But what if I told you that it isn't ABOUT you, unless of course you actually have something to contribute, in which case you are very welcome. Do you?
